<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I was highly recommended Robert Fagles&apos; Iliad. I enjoyed the work he did there and at the Odyssey, so when looking for the Theban Plays, I got his tra<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I was highly recommended Robert Fagles' Iliad. I enjoyed the work he did there and at the Odyssey, so when looking for the Theban Plays, I got his translation again.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
