<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer1095755195686878569">Sophocles (born c. 496 bc, Colonus, near Athens [Greece]—died 406, Athens), (Greek: <b>
  <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/17597623.________' title='Σοφοκλής' rel='nofollow noopener'>Σοφοκλής</a>
</b>; German editions: <b>
